        <p class="ca-prose" data-reveal>
          With uniform values it reads like a grid exploding. Add the randomness
          from the talk — varied lifetimes, radii, velocities, and a
          noise-driven sideways drift biased 75% one way — and it finally looks
          like dust:
        </p>
        <pre class="ca-code" data-reveal><code>{codeRandom}</code></pre>
      </div>
